part of speech = ថ្នាក់ពាក្យ

C. understanding parts of speech write the part of speech of the words  in these sentences.
Dont use a dictionary.

1. Taylors textbook looks quire colorful.
- looks = Verb
- quite = Ädverb
- colorful = Adjective

2. Students absolutely defuse their textbooks.
-Student = Nount
- defuse = Verb
- textbooks = Noun

3. An essential study skill is knowing how to mark a book.
- essential = Adjecrtive
- skill = Noun
- mark = Verb 


-----------------------
al = adjective
ce = nount


